  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8eafb6d5-3da1-4414-8aac-aaf7b227e351",
    "name": "Simplifier.net FHIR Package API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "API to find and retrieve all publicly published FHIR packages.\n* Serves all FHIR packages from Simplifier.net, HL7 International and other public feeds\n* For humans there is the [FHIR Registry at registry.fhir.org](https://registry.fhir.org/) for searching the full package library.\n\nFind the documentation for [other Simplifier.net APIs](https://docs.fire.ly/projects/Simplifier/api.html).\n",
